CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

August 14, 2006

[Cite as 08/14/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-4140.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2006-1289. State ex rel. Marcum v. Corzine.

In Mandamus and Prohibition. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed.

Moyee, C.J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
